CONDITIONS ON DISTRIBUTION AND MODIFICATION
============================================

  1. Activities other than distribution and/or modification of the Work
are not covered by this license; they are outside its scope.  In
particular, the act of running the Work is not restricted and no
requirements are made concerning any offers of support for the Work.

  2. You are allowed to distribute a complete, unmodified copy of the Work
as you received it.  Distribution of only part of the Work is considered
modification of the Work, and no right to distribute such a Derived Work
may be assumed under the terms of this clause.

  3. You are allowed to distribute a Compiled Work that has been generated
from a complete, unmodified copy of the Work.  Distribution of only part
of such a Compiled Work is considered modification of the Compiled Work,
and no right to distribute such a Derived Compiled Work may be assumed
under the terms of this clause.

  4. If you are not the Current Maintainer of the Work, you are allowed to
distribute a Derived Work provided the following conditions are met for
every component of the Work unless that component clearly states that
the terms under which it may be modified or distributed do not include
the conditions described in this clause:

    a. The derived component is distributed with a name different from
       that of the corresponding component of the Work.

    b. The combined distribution is accompanied by a statement that
       documents all changes made to the Work.

    c. The combined distribution is accompanied by a statement that
       informs recipients of the location of the unchanged Work.

  5. No additional conditions may be placed on the distribution of the Work,
Derived Works, or Compiled Works.

